Teodor Melescanu, Presidential Adviser Traian Chebeleu and 
Varujan Vosganian, deputy in the Romanian Parliament 
representing the Armenian minority of Romania. 
  Armenian ambassador Guergui Kazinyan [name as received] 
presented on Monday, April 18, his credentials while the 
Armenian Embassy in Bucharest is going to be officially opened 
within the following days. 

