  [Text] Paris, April 21 (AFP) -- Two rockets hit a Gorazde 
hospital building Thursday, killing 20 patients and visitors, 
the medical aid charity Medecins Sans Frontieres (MSF) said. 
MSF released the information after speaking with its staff in 
the besieged Moslem enclave. 

