<H3> <TI>   Bosnian Serbs Attack Croat Areas </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Bosnian Serbs Attack Croat Areas </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD2004172894 Zagreb Radio Croatia Network in Serbo-Croatian 
1700 GMT 20 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2004172894 </F>
<F P=104>  Zagreb Radio Croatia Network </F>
<F P=105>  Serbo-Croatian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Bosnian Serbs launched three artillery attacks on 
Zupanja and Bosnjaci at around 1445 today. The early warning 
center in Zupanja sounded a general alert at 1445 and again at 
1600, when a second attack began. A third attack began at 1650. 
Most of the shells landed in the Zupanja area. According to 
the reports we have received so far, dozens of mortar shells 
were fired on Zupanja and Bosnjaci, causing considerable 
material damage. Nobody was injured in the attacks. 

</TEXT>

