<F P=102> AU2004181494 Bucharest Radio Romania Network in Romanian 
1700 GMT 20 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> AU2004181494 </F>
<F P=104>  Bucharest Radio Romania Network </F>
<F P=105>  Romanian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Romanian President Ion Iliescu and Yasir 'Arafat, 
chairman of the PLO Executive Committee, held talks at Cotroceni 
Palace this afternoon in the presence of their two delegations. 
In a statement to journalists after the talks, Iliescu welcomed 
the Palestinian leader's presence in Bucharest and the fact that 
the Crans Montana Forum offers the opportunity for a meeting 
between 'Arafat and Israeli Foreign Minister Shim'on Peres, who 
