<F P=106> [Unattributed report: "Additional Serbian Army Forces </F>
Deployed in Dragas"] 
  [Text] Alongside with the frequent movements of the 
Serbian army throughout Kosova, additional units of these forces 
have been recently deployed in the areas adjacent to Albania. 
Today's BUJKU reports that over the last couple of days several 
additional units of the Serbian army have been brought in the 
military barracks in Dragas (town near the Kosovo-Albania 
border). As reported, the Serbian army has recently commenced 
to amend and repair the military barracks near the border, which 
have not been used for decades. 

