<H4>    TANJUG: Muslims Reject Cease-Fire </H4>

<F P=102> LD2204115194 Belgrade TANJUG Domestic Service in 
Serbo-Croatian 1041 GMT 22 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2204115194 </F>
<F P=104>  Belgrade TANJUG Domestic Service </F>
